      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "The children of Israel gave — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Probably they gave the Levites promiscuously such cities as God commanded, and the lot appropriated them to their several houses or families. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Out of their inheritance — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "That is, out of their several possessions, that the burden might be equally divided; and that the Levites, being dispersed among the several tribes, according to Jacob’s prediction, (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Genesis 49:7",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ",) might more easily and effectually ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "teach ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Israelites God’s law and judgments, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "which they were engaged to do, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Deuteronomy 33:10",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; and that the people might upon all occasions resort to them, and ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "inquire ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "the meaning ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "of the law at their mouths. And suburbs — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Not only the use, but the absolute dominion of them, as is manifest both from ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Joshua 21:11-12",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", where a distinction is made between the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "city and suburbs of Hebron, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and the ",
        "children": []
