        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And the children of Israel gave",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] The successor of Moses did not fail to carry out faithfully the Divine Command, and preparations were made for assigning to them certain cities for their possession.",
        "children": []
